<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>龙脉文化 · 水晶能量商城</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <style>
        /* 商城特有样式 */
        .crystals-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .crystals-hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .crystals-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px 60px;
        }

        .crystal-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .crystal-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .crystal-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 220px;
            object-fit: cover;
            background: #f5f7fa;
        }

        .crystal-info {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .crystal-name {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .crystal-desc {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .crystal-tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .crystal-tag {
            background: #e8f0fe;
            color: #667eea;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .crystal-price {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #f39c12;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .buy-btn {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .buy-btn:hover {
            background: #5568d3;
        }

        .footer-note {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .footer-note a {
            color: #667eea;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>🦞 龙脉文化</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">天然水晶 · 能量认证 · 保真假一赔十</p>
        </header>

        <div class="crystals-hero">
            <h1>💎 水晶能量商城</h1>
            <p>精选天然水晶，能量加持，助运改命</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.9;">
                所有产品支持闲鱼担保交易 · 7天无理由退换
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="crystals-grid">
            <!-- 产品1：白水晶 -->
            <div class="crystal-card">
                <img class="crystal-img" src="images/crystals/white-crystal.jpg" alt="白水晶手链">
                <div class="crystal-info">
                    <div class="crystal-name">白水晶手链</div>
                    <div class="crystal-desc">
                        天然白水晶，净化负能量，提升专注力。适合初学者入门，净化空间磁场。
                    </div>
                    <div class="crystal-tags">
                        <span class="crystal-tag">净化</span>
                        <span class="crystal-tag">入门</span>
                        <span class="crystal-tag">专注</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="crystal-price">¥99</div>
                    <a href="https://2.taobao.com/item.htm?id=待上架" target="_blank" class="buy-btn">
                        🛒 去闲鱼购买
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 产品2：紫水晶 -->
            <div class="crystal-card">
                <img class="crystal-img" src="https://picsum.photos/seed/amethyst/400/300" alt="紫水晶手链">
                <div class="crystal-info">
                    <div class="crystal-name">紫水晶手链</div>
                    <div class="crystal-desc">
                        乌拉圭紫水晶，助眠安神，提升直觉力。适合需要灵感创意的人群。
                    </div>
                    <div class="crystal-tags">
                        <span class="crystal-tag">助眠</span>
                        <span class="crystal-tag">直觉</span>
                        <span class="crystal-tag">灵感</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="crystal-price">¥199</div>
                    <a href="https://2.taobao.com/item.htm?id=待上架" target="_blank" class="buy-btn">
                        🛒 去闲鱼购买
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 产品3：绿幽灵 -->
            <div class="crystal-card">
                <img class="crystal-img" src="https://picsum.photos/seed/green-ghost/400/300" alt="绿幽灵手链">
                <div class="crystal-info">
                    <div class="crystal-name">绿幽灵手链</div>
                    <div class="crystal-desc">
                        哥伦比亚绿幽灵，正财招财，事业上升。适合创业者、职场人士佩戴。
                    </div>
                    <div class="crystal-tags">
                        <span class="crystal-tag">正财</span>
                        <span class="crystal-tag">事业</span>
                        <span class="crystal-tag">晋升</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="crystal-price">¥299</div>
                    <a href="https://2.taobao.com/item.htm?id=待上架" target="_blank" class="buy-btn">
                        🛒 去闲鱼购买
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 产品4：黑曜石 -->
            <div class="crystal-card">
                <img class="crystal-img" src="https://picsum.photos/seed/obsidian/400/300" alt="黑曜石手链">
                <div class="crystal-info">
                    <div class="crystal-name">黑曜石手链</div>
                    <div class="crystal-desc">
                        墨西哥黑曜石，强力辟邪，防小人。适合磁场敏感、常走夜路的人群。
                    </div>
                    <div class="crystal-tags">
                        <span class="crystal-tag">辟邪</span>
                        <span class="crystal-tag">防小人</span>
                        <span class="crystal-tag">防护</span>
                    </div>
